{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017ULFcyKFmaht6UQxhEigX2","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have everything I need. Let me plan the steps:\n\n1. Extract CA cert and key from the `mongodb-tls-ca` secret\n2. Copy them to the openssl-toolbox pod\n3. Generate a new server key and CSR with all the required SANs\n4. Sign the CSR with the CA (1 year validity)\n5. Create server.pem (key + cert concatenated - MongoDB format)\n6. Update the `mongodb-tls-cert` secret\n7. Rolling restart the StatefulSet\n\nThe SANs needed are: `localhost`, `mongo`, `mongo.mongodb`, `mongo.mongodb.svc`, `mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local`, `mongo-rs-0.mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local`, `mongo-rs-1.mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local`, `mongo-rs-2.mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local`\nI'll work through this using the openssl-toolbox pod to handle the certificate operations.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1436,"cache_read_input_tokens":32019,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1436},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0fd00ace-6ea2-40ce-8df7-1b357a13abb0","uuid":"22152b9f-c663-4038-ba22-a73ac19d1235","request_id":"req_011CcQ5WrDWTnbFPk41ZWhog"}
